a card is a thing
a pile is a thing

to say (message = "no")
	print the message
say "No"

to proclaim (reply as text)
	print the reply
proclaim "yo"

to notify with message
	print the message + "!!!"
notify with message = "YO"

to shout with message as text
	print the message + "!!!"
shout with message = "YO"

to confirm (message as text) with reply = "unsure"
	print the message
	print the reply
confirm  "Really"
confirm "Really" with reply = "No"

to play (a card) on (a pile)
	set the pile of the card to the pile
play a new card with foo = "bar" on a new pile

